Invocation Name: pregnancy facts
des:
Pregnancy is one of the most wonderful process of human nature. The Pregnancy Facts And Tips skill's goal is to help you understand this stage. You can ask Alexa for facts or tips. If you want to listen a fact, just say, "Give me a fact". Alexa can also give you helpful tips on pregnancy, you can say something like, "I need a tip".

This skill will help you understand pregnancy the right way, you will be amazed about the wonderful facts Alexa can give you and the helpful tips you will receive.
